{"tid":748254,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[ezone] 日本節目測試冷氣 開足24小時比5小時內重啟省電環保","createTime":"2018-07-19T05:21:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-29T23:36:28.000Z","uid":55981,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b94f2ea4cbbc5be8a0452e7489b29fc7a2cc09ed","tid":748254,"uid":55981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T05:21:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2118032/%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E6%B8%AC%E8%A9%A6%E5%86%B7%E6%B0%A3%2024%20%E5%B0%8F%E6%99%82%E9%95%B7%E9%96%8B%E6%9B%B4%E7%9C%81%E9%9B%BB%EF%BC%9F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2118032%2F%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC%25E6%25B8%25AC%25E8%25A9%25A6%25E5%2586%25B7%25E6%25B0%25A3%252024%2520%25E5%25B0%258F%25E6%2599%2582%25E9%2595%25B7%25E9%2596%258B%25E6%259B%25B4%25E7%259C%2581%25E9%259B%25BB%25EF%25BC%259F&d=ffeL2UZe1D0zqWnfAH%2BT1f%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=0e56c14e\" target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2118032/%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E6%B8%AC%E8%A9%A6%E5%86%B7%E6%B0%A3%2024%20%E5%B0%8F%E6%99%82%E9%95%B7%E9%96%8B%E6%9B%B4%E7%9C%81%E9%9B%BB%EF%BC%9F</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n開冷氣所造成的碳排放不少，為了應對溫室效應，不少環保團體都不建議冷氣長開。但原來，長開冷氣似乎會比一開一關更省電？近日網上瘋傳日本綜藝節目在一年前做的測試。該測試顯示，當「冷氣 24 小時不關更省電」，但就要達成一個時間上的先決條件！<br />\n<br />\n日本綜藝節目在一年前做了一個測試，看看是 24 小時不關冷氣，還是一開一關冷氣更加省電。實測結果出乎意料，若關冷氣後 5 小時 27 分内會再次重啟，就倒不如 24 小時不關冷氣，因爲這樣反而更省電。所以，<span style=\"color: red;\">如果只是出門 1、2 小時的話，不如就讓冷氣開著吧；但如果出門超過 5 小時半，冷氣還是關了吧</span>。這亦代表正常情況下，「冷氣 24 小時不關更省電」並不夠準確，因爲這樣做只會造成電費更高。<br />\n<br />\n爲什麽會這樣呢？原來冷氣在開機之初最「扯電」，但市内溫度下降後耗電量就會慢慢變小。經過專家精確計算後，就找出了「5 小時 27 分」這個數字，但這只是日本的情況。畢竟香港跟日本的氣候環境不同，而冷氣機型號、種類不同亦有影響。所以與其精確計算省電，不如盡量「避免密集開關冷氣」。如只是出門 1、2 小時，就可以樣冷氣開著但調高幾度；若長時間不在家，還是把冷氣關掉吧。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2115000/2118032/air1_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2115000%2F2118032%2Fair1_600.jpg&h=cb33f823&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日本電視台實測「空調 24 小時不關是否更省電」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2115000/2118032/air4_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2115000%2F2118032%2Fair4_600.jpg&h=53908f33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n專家坦言，「空調 24 小時不關更省電」只會造成電費更高<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2115000/2118032/air2_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2115000%2F2118032%2Fair2_600.jpg&h=bcad2ad3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n若關冷氣後 5 小時 27 分内會再次重啟，不如 24 小時不關冷氣"},{"pid":"04c688b14c8d9254fd8ddd5139d9e950da5e9440","tid":748254,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T05:24:18.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"d02a33e32956ba6f9c845bd3424c7ed8aa86ac61","tid":748254,"uid":17103,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T05:24:55.000Z","msg":"實踐是驗證真理唯一方法, 講果個國家做唔到但係人地日本仔就做得到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1024d1df7a1a9e27cf3e091eb496abac5c60a556","tid":748254,"uid":55981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T05:27:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zzclX8pmYa4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DzzclX8pmYa4&d=ffeL2UZe1D0zqWnfAH%2BT1f%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=88c7d471\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zzclX8pmYa4</a><br />\n<br />\n差條片sor"},{"pid":"bc072a92df201de9e4dd8e1c6510c15b352c5d74","tid":748254,"uid":57035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T01:12:46.000Z","msg":"環保狗：所以應該開風扇就算"},{"pid":"ee0600e9dc34e146a2e7378f7f38ae44215d7750","tid":748254,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike